==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Glover
<hw>Glov"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One whose trade it is
to make or sell gloves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><mcol><col><b>Glover's suture</b></col> <it>or</it>
<col><b>Glover's stitch</b></col></mcol>, <cd>a kind of stitch used in
sewing up wounds, in which the thread is drawn alternately through each
side from within outward.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Glow</ent>⟦br⟧
